{"tid":156049,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[HEHE]一副勝利笑容，離開酒店","createTime":"2017-03-14T12:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T12:58:35.000Z","uid":8810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"769666f51ae27e42cda1bf98ccff5ebc6c6d8d38","tid":156049,"uid":8810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T12:58:35.000Z","msg":"七年前，無綫電視前業務總經理陳志雲，同前經理人叢培崑，被指收受利益，官司纏繞不休。今日陳志雲上訴得值，折騰的日子終於劃上句號。 <br />\n<br />\n今早陳志雲離開法庭，與七年來為他撐遮擋雨，口中的守護天使王喜，及寵將梁泰萊等人，<span style=\"color: red;\">先到中環文華酒店歇一</span>歇，之後殺落旺角朗豪酒店食飯慶祝。 <br />\n<br />\n甩官司一身輕的他，雖然離開時沒再發表感受，只拋下兩句：「冇嘢再補充，我依家仲有嘢要做。」便匆匆登上七人車，但他的笑容，完全感受到冀盼七年，霧霾終於有散去的一天！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=2_487227_0&amp;i=20170314\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D2_487227_0%26i%3D20170314&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWdWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=ee6d8daa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D2_487227_0%26i%3D20170314&h=0b11786c\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=2_487227_0&amp;i=20170314</a>"}]}